import React from 'react' import { useState, useEffect } from 'react' import { Table, TableHeader,TableRow, TableHeaderCell,TableBody, TableCell, TableFooter, Menu, MenuItem,Icon } from 'semantic-ui-react' import CarService from '../services/carService' export default function CarList() { const [cars, setCars] = useState([]) useEffect(() => { let carService = new CarService(); carService.getCars() .then(result => setCars(result.data.data)) .catch(error => console.error("Arabaları getirirken hata oluştu:", error)); }, []); return (
Kilometer Plate Year Daily Price Model Name Color Name {cars.map(car=>( {car.kilometer} {car.plate} {car.year} {car.dailyPrice} {car.modelName} {car.colorName} ))} 1 2 3 4
) }
